name: PERSONALIZED SONG (Temporarily Unavailable)
description:
What you'll get: 
1. A personalized recording of a Yeltsin classic song with your name (or your friend's name) incorporated in the lyrics. 
2. An album cover featuring your face with the members of SSLYBY (we'll email you a JPEG and you can print it off and stick it in a jewel case)

What we need from you: 
1. A short bio about your friend 
2. Pick your favorite SSLYBY song 
2. A JPEG of your friend's face

-we'll send you a rough draft of the song to see if you'd like any mixing or lyrical changes

- Send your JPEG and short bio to us at SSLYBY@gmail.com

-Some songs are not available. Email us your request and we'll let you know if it will work or not.
